rove hose life</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">No moving parts in the fluid stream</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Inexpensive to maintain &ndash; no valves, seals or glands</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Pumps are reversible and can be used to empty lines or clear blockages</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Integral drive and motor can run as low as 1 rpm</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Compact design, ideal for tight spaces and flexible placement</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">&ldquo;Quick change&rdquo; one-piece hose clamp assembly</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Quick replacement of hose and lube</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><strong>EP Cross Reference</strong><br />\r\n	Eccentric pumps directly cross over to Graco Hose pumps with the following:</span></span></p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 540px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; width: 206px; height: 143px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><strong>Eccentric Pump<